{"analytics_identifier":null,"base_path":"/government/organisations/government-office-for-technology-transfer/about/membership","content_id":"954108b9-7bc5-4bf7-b0a0-578953f5f885","description":"","details":{"attachments":[],"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"gott-advisory-board\">GOTT Advisory Board</h2>\n\n<p>GOTT’s advisory board supports the Chief Executive and leadership team by advising on long term strategy, annual planning and performance.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"knowledge-assets-network\">Knowledge Assets Network</h2>\n\n<p>The Knowledge Assets Network is a community for those who work with or who want to learn more about Knowledge Assets in central government, arm’s length bodies and public sector research establishments. The <abbr title=\"Knowledge Assets Network\">KAN</abbr> provides a space for members to share advice, best practice, challenges, insights and to learn from one another about Knowledge Asset management.</p>\n\n<p>Visit the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/join-the-knowledge-assets-network-for-the-public-sector/the-knowledge-asset-network\">Knowledge Assets Network</a> for more information.</p>\n\n<p>For questions, email us at <a href=\"mailto:GOTT@dsit.gov.uk\">GOTT@dsit.gov.uk</a>.</p>\n\n</div>","change_history":[{"note":"First published.","public_timestamp":"2022-10-04T14:42:12Z"}],"headers":[{"id":"gott-advisory-board","level":2,"text":"GOTT Advisory Board"},{"id":"knowledge-assets-network","level":2,"text":"Knowledge Assets Network"}],"organisation":"b9e7b282-1c89-4c2f-9aff-35b258a5bab5","tags":{"browse_pages":[]}},"document_type":"membership","first_published_at":"2022-10-04T15:42:12+01:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/government-office-for-technology-transfer/about/membership","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/government-office-for-technology-transfer/about/membership","base_path":"/government/organisations/government-office-f